{"tid":640887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"300人晚會聲援理大被兜導師 馮偉華轟校方衰過商界","createTime":"2018-04-24T15:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T15:32:37.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99d86bef276bc61b66bff1c73805a8930353e3dc","tid":640887,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/231617_71abf6bd55122ea775c33acd4dfec03b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F231617_71abf6bd55122ea775c33acd4dfec03b.png&h=391b313d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/231624_1243a806ffdd3715b202fb834843e25a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F231624_1243a806ffdd3715b202fb834843e25a.png&h=a2c26b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/231627_70b31e87b944f318e1a8314a04c56332.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F231627_70b31e87b944f318e1a8314a04c56332.png&h=6ef4fa9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n理工大學應用社會科學系以財赤為由「兜走」負責實習督導的9名半職導師。理大應用社會科學系系會聯同理大學生會晚上（24日）舉辦晚會，由被炒的半職導師之一項志銘作為代表向師生交代被裁的細節，獲得逾300師生校友、教協會長馮偉華及立法會議員張超雄、邵家臻等人出席聲援。<br />\n<br />\n項志銘直言，一班半職導師在理大年資介乎18年至23年，全部對理大有極深感情及歸屬感，以他自己為例，明年便屆理大的退休年齡，一直以「做到退休」為心願，卻被學系在此關頭將他裁走，極為痛心。<br />\n<br />\n會上又播出數段受影響導師的錄音，有女導師自嘲「太天真」，為理大貢獻多年卻無情裁走；又有導師寄語學生畢業後就職時「唔好做奴材」，要時刻保留對社工工作的熱情。<br />\n<br />\n應社系系會在晚會後舉辦論壇，探討本港大學重研究、輕教學，屢向負責教學的人員開刀。教協指早前曾協助受影響導師約見校方，會上有校方高層直接承認裁減人手決定「只為慳錢」，更聲稱歡迎被裁導師之後再應徵「件工制」、薪酬福利大減的兼任導師。<br />\n<br />\n論壇嘉賓之一、有份出席會面的教協會長馮偉華炮轟校方「赤裸承認要導師攞低啲人工、做相同工作」，做法拙劣粗暴，連商界都不如。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》沙士15周年系列網站，正式登場：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2F&d=as9LQJ0q1zqmooOgAV5qMBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=884e5c14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2F&h=1028b085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/</a><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180424/58114158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58114158&d=as9LQJ0q1zqmooOgAV5qMBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=fc430ba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58114158&h=911b85d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180424/58114158</a>"},{"pid":"048c7fcf33c26f99a61247260abd6772c2a54bc3","tid":640887,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"算吧啦 poly係咁架啦"},{"pid":"7dbeb04f7dd24d61d48dcc099b135149d9b800b0","tid":640887,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88282881eb87b51f4b4c973f912ca98e252637b0","tid":640887,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"048c7fcf33c26f99a61247260abd6772c2a54bc3","tid":640887,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"算吧啦 poly係咁架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"近年香港社福學術界發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n之前shitty又話cut 社工pt degree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}